attributes.attribute: JD.com is Chinas largest online retailer and its biggest overall retailer, as well as the countrys biggest Internet company by revenue. JD.com sets the standard for online shopping through its commitment to quality, authenticity, and its vast product offering covering everything from fresh food and apparel to electronics and cosmetics. Its unrivalled nationwide fulfillment network covers 99% of Chinas population, and provides standard same- and next-day delivery - a level of service and speed that is unmatched globally.
